{"type": "article", "id": 32662, "title": "啊，Snapchat 推出可以拍 10 秒视频的太阳眼镜 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-27T02:45:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12352, "name": "奢侈品电商"}, {"id": 33206, "name": "欧洲股票市场"}, {"id": 33207, "name": "智能太阳眼镜"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 1746, "name": "Snapchat"}, {"id": 3865, "name": "adidas Originals"}, {"id": 12792, "name": "Neiman Marcus"}, {"id": 17255, "name": "KITH"}, {"id": 31426, "name": "Carhartt WIP"}, {"id": 33208, "name": "Certona"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160927083146gtbe3OExAUVdzZWI.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/european-stock-markets-slide-mulberry-boohoo-10565827/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国大选首场辩论前日，欧洲股票市场大跌</b></a> | 其中，零售业和奢侈品业的股价也有所下滑。Hugo Boss 的股价下降了 2.3%，至 49.40 欧元。Mulberry 集团的股价下滑了 2.8%，至 11 英镑。Salvatore Ferragamo 下滑了 2.1%，至 22.11 欧元。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.finsmes.com/2016/09/certona-secures-30m-in-venture-capital-funding.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Certona 获 3000 万美元融资</b></a> | Certona 成立于 2004 年，利用云技术为全球五百多家顶级电商服务。它提供多渠道的个人零售体验升级方案，其独特的算法可以准确预测消费者的购物倾向。此次，它获得了来自私募基金 Primus 的 3000 万美元融资。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/business/earnings/neiman-marcus-q4-2016-earnings-sales-profit-revenues-karen-katz-261950/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国高档连锁百货 Neiman Marcus 业绩持续下滑</b></a>  |  Neiman Marcus 第四财政季度（第三自然季度）营收下降 3.3%，至 11.3 亿美元，其中，销售下降了 4.1%，净亏损 4.07 亿美元，去年同期净亏损为 3290 万美元。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/trends-analysis/ralph-lauren-top-spot-pmx-report-10566054/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Ralph Lauren 是电商表现最好的奢侈品牌</b></a> | 据研究机构 PMX 的报告所称，Ralph Lauren 的电子商务销售额在总营业额中的占比为 19.2%，是电商表现最好的奢侈品牌。排名第二的是 Michael Kors，它的电商销售额占比为 18.5%。Coach、LV、Gucci 紧随其后，分别为 12%、9.5%、5.3%。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">荷兰品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/patta-x-carhartt-wip-2016-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Patta 再度与 Carhartt WIP 合作</a>，带来了一系列结合街头风格和工装风的单品，包括连帽衫、夹克、T-shirt、针织帽、斜挎包等。该联名系列将于 9 月 30 日发售。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927093932vLaVWwNcuq73nxKf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666302\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927093932DcmEYxFwrAK01Lgb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666993\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927093932glkQCUfHIm1OvJEM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666302\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927093932mvPgMNAndfYiOVXH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666302\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927093932LSTNbHPeghazUoFJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666302\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609270939339kwirOHTyblngX0d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666993\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927093933fhWydGMrYJ2gNwZS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666302\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609270939336wLKF89TOBvRx7QV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666993\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927093933HJfG6s5jRCbZaTvU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666302\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927093947X8lWc7LFrCPE5dqg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666302\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927093947ngl1hRkirC93zFwu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666993\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>想让运动变得更时尚，KITH 正式发布 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/kith-women-2016-fall-winter-activewear\" rel=\"nofollow\">KITH Women 2016</a> 秋季运动系列。带来了多款 Sport Bra，以及两款运动风衣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094004Ahj497UyVG6WgvrS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666459\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609270940045pWc8RYmfMinyQ6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667082\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094004kmEOGVN5UsZHXa9t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666459\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094005u1Z5fdIhaB4yVK0F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666459\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094005EZH8sKDxOcNJm9ad.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666459\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094005O3i6Ycl9HJyBvGPf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666459\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094018uF50mX1IjkLeqZnW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666459\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">来看 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/hm-fall2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">H&amp;M 2016</a> 秋季新品。该系列宣扬一种 70 年代的浪漫，注入了印花、宫廷风立领等元素，将于 9 月 29 日正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094029dFzRq2HWJ6TQE5fk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094029CZi3r0FIwbc6JH8o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609270940290rYOpIxAuCQDbXEn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094029YcQqjnbLGkE7axph.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094029O5sqy1apL2BMk0R7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609270940309HtFnZrkT2h4AwKj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Snapchat 推出首款太阳眼镜 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/gadgets/spectacles-by-snapchat/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spectacles</a>。该眼镜的镜片两角处有一个小镜头，每按一次可以录制 10 秒影像。镜头采用 115 度视野角度，接近人的视线范围。该款眼镜定价 130 美元，分别有蓝色、黑色、橙红色三种颜色。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609270940529rcmC07tMflSuHUY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094109pUSsj0rHKZ8lL1iM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094109V2FfPi31XanUdbvj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094120nDBVyKmsraHuIj16.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094128Tkqf9z6W7L8EnNHt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/adidas-originals-pharrell-hu-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Originals 与 PHARRELL WILLIAMS 的合作系列 Hu </a>完整公开。从 Play For The Human Race 这个主题出发，该系列试图表达传颂一种文化的多样性，探索人性的本质。这个系列将于 9 月 29 日正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094158FEUcyto4rL1MjTHw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094200QFEABhGJfzeH71aN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094210DYq7HkCiKOflg4XN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609270942154RQ7oUjxHdPJDSAW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094215ovpTEhWjnJxdryVY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094215hLIX2EJq65peK3QV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094215J1QLxMC4g2bw8Nz5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160927094216srILlz8OfyeD0YUA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p>"}